3
00:00:04,000 --> 00:00:06,000
Sol Ultra Gearbox verifies what actually ran.

4
00:00:06,000 --> 00:00:07,750
It routes Codex work

5
00:00:07,750 --> 00:00:09,500
to typed Sol,

6
00:00:09,500 --> 00:00:11,250
Terra, and Luna

7
00:00:11,250 --> 00:00:13,000
